UID:vJbmoNcQnupuvDIUQfX4o
SUMMARY:Meet the Cossacks: Seattle's Motorcycle Stunt and Drill Team
DTSTAMP:20260315T172854Z
DTSTART:20260418T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Dive into the history of the Cossacks\\\, Seattle’s long stroll
	ing Motorcycle Stunt and Drill Team\\\, with Rob Root and other members. S
	ince 1938\\\, the Seattle Cossacks have captured the imagination of audien
	ces with great pyramids and other wonders of the motorcycling world. Follo
	wing the presentation\\\, visitors are welcome to get up close and persona
	l for photos with the team’s vintage Harleys! \\nTickets for this program 
	are free\\\, but do not include access to MOHAI’s exhibitions. If you woul
	d like to see all that MOHAI has to offer during your visit\\\, you can pu
	rchase museum admission here. \\nFor more accessibility support\\\, email 
	programs@mohai.org two weeks before the program.\n\nhttps://mohai.org/even
	t/meet-the-cossacks-seattles-motorcycle-stunt-and-drill-team/\n\nFrom MOHA
	I - Museum of History & Industry
URL:https://mohai.org/event/meet-the-cossacks-seattles-motorcycle-stunt-and
	-drill-team/
LOCATION:Microsoft Lakefront Pavilion\\\, MOHAI - 860 Terry Ave N\\\, Seatt
	le\\\, WA\\\, 98109\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:mohai
CATEGORIES:MOHAI - Museum of History & Industry
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
